videos.headline: Wake Forest hits pass over middle for 9-yd TD

videos.description: Florida State Seminoles running back Cam Aker blasts through a hole for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.description: Florida State Semioles WR Keith Gavin breaks a tackle on a 49-yard reception but fumbles it on the way to the end zone, giving Wake Forest the ball.

videos.description: After Florida State fumbled away a sure TD, Stanford Samuels makes up for it by intercepting Wake Forest to set up RB Jacques Patrick for a short touchdown.
